(g)	 in the case of a member of the Board in paragraph
60(1)(d), if he absents himself from three consecutive
meetings of the Board without leave in writing of the
Chairman;
(h)	 if his appointment is revoked by the Minister;
(i)	 if his resignation is accepted by the Minister; or
(j)	 if the Minister is satisfied that he absents himself from
three consecutive meetings of the Institute without leave
or reasonable excuse.
